<card>
<h2 id="color" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#color" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Color</h2>
<p>Use the color property to change the base color of the component and some of the child components, to better understand the handling of colors and themes you can see it <RouterLink to="/docs/theme/">here</RouterLink></p>
<p>Allowed values â€‹â€‹are:</p>
<ul>
<li>primary</li>
<li>success</li>
<li>danger</li>
<li>warning</li>
<li>dark</li>
<li>RGB</li>
<li>HEX</li>
</ul>
